name: SHE SAYD - Kay Joe Ft. Tania Paz
description:
When Dario Adames, former drummer of Caramelos de Cianuro, one of the most important rock bands in Venezuela, and now the founder of BigUp Records Club, was walking on the streets of Wynwood during the Art Basel in Miami in 2020, he met Kay Joe AKA the Real Unscripted, a street artist who was demonstrating his real flow in the midst of the crowd of people walking through the area. Dario invited him to the studio and this song came out. 

After that day in another experience, during a Jam session in a place called OAK Garden in Miami's downtown, a blonde from Madrid came up spontaneously to sing, Dario, impressed by both talents, managed to bring them together and SHE SAYD was born, A love of two strangers united by a song. 

A true NFT that kicks off a new life for BigUp Records Club. Welcome to the club! 

MINTED OCTOBER 3rd 2021 - ONLY FOR PERSONAL USE
